{"type": "article", "id": 9947, "title": "野餐用红酒杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-25T08:02:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155727hNE5CkeWHu9LBrnj.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t阿姆斯特丹设计师 Ramona Enache 设计了一款在野餐时用的红酒杯，与普通酒杯不同的是，为了避免杯子倾倒，设计师把杯底做成了一根金属钉，方便使用者无论在草地上还是山里面，都可以轻松插进土壤或石头缝里面。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"http://www.tothepointer.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155723pAD3RQGdtH5TZr8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155723yzSx34Oc5CrhY9pm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155724h7NdAqZ5DHkEK64R.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155724UnNckbQMVwXirZ0l.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155725iaBcgXmeYGnuCA9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155725I1CtWRidjKPZp2nr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061557268c9N7YJnAQVskMo0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}